Training and professional development
• Organise training programs for medical and non-medical staff to improve skills and service quality.
• Support the continuous professional development of doctors, nurses, and laboratory personnel.
• Facilitate the orientation and integration of newly recruited staff.
Organizational coordination
• Work closely with the CEO, Director, and department heads to align human resources with operational needs.
• Ensure effective coordination between clinical teams, laboratory staff, and call-centre personnel.
• Contribute to improving staff motivation, workplace culture, and organisational efficiency.
